title: 08/10/21 DPS Hour 1 Sean Salisbury
itunes:title: 08/10/21 DPS Hour 1 Sean Salisbury
description:
Former NFL QB Sean Salisbury joins the show, and he tells Dan Patrick that he would not trade embattled Texans QB Deshaun Watson if it was up to him! Plus, why people can't tell Kirk Cousins to get vaccinated if he doesn't want to get it.
